title: Dire Straits - Ticket to Heaven (1992) [FLAC]
description:
Maybe the best live recording of a Dire Straits concert ever - to me much better than the official live albums 'Alchemy', 'On the Night' and 'Live at the BBC'. Excellent sound quality, the band at it's best and a stunning audience





Dire Straits - Ticket to Heaven
Label: Big Music - BIG 22/23

recorded live, Basel, Switzerland
June 28, 1992


unofficial soundboard recording - excellent quality


Disc 1:

   1. Calling Elvis
   2. Walk of Life
   3. Heavy Fuel
   4. Romeo and Juliet
   5. The Bug
   6. Private Investigation
   7. Sultans of Swing
   8. Your Latest Trick 

Disc 2:

   1. On Every Street
   2. Two Young Lovers
   3. Telegraph Road
   4. Money For Nothing
   5. Brothers in Arms
   6. Solid Rock
   7. Going Home 



Lineup:

Mark Knopfler - guitar, vocals
John Illsey - bass, vocals
Phil Palmer - guitar, vocals
Paul Franklin - pedal steel guitar
Alan Clark - keyboards
Guy Fletcher - keyboard, vocals
Chris White - saxophone, vocals
Chris Whitten - drums
Danny Cummings - percussion, vocals
